# 💰 Finance Dashboard

A modern and responsive Finance Dashboard web application to track income, expenses, and financial insights.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📊 View total balance, income, and expenses
- 📈 Interactive charts (Line Chart & Pie Chart)
- 🔍 Filter transactions by type and category
- 🌙 Dark / Light theme toggle
- 👤 Role-based UI (Viewer / Admin)
- 📋 Transaction listing with insights

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- ⚛️ React.js
- ⚡ Vite
- 🎨 CSS (Custom Styling)
- 📊 Recharts (for charts)
- 🔗 React Router DOM
- 💾 Local Storage (for user data & theme)

